{"tid":505424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南非 - 每年有近10萬名男性慘遭強姦","createTime":"2017-12-21T05:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T01:14:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d0eb05c2fa484c2e9ea63b600d0a4126c2dbdf3","tid":505424,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/142046/%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E25%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A9%E5%A9%A6%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E6%8F%AD%E5%85%A9%E6%88%90%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B7%E6%80%A7-%E7%96%91%E6%B6%89%E6%95%A3%E6%92%AD%E6%84%9B%E6%BB%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F142046%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259D%259E25%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6-%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2595%25A3%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%25BB%258B&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8922c1cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/142046/%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E25%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A9%E5%A9%A6%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E6%8F%AD%E5%85%A9%E6%88%90%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B7%E6%80%A7-%E7%96%91%E6%B6%89%E6%95%A3%E6%92%AD%E6%84%9B%E6%BB%8B</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>組織「南非男性性侵生還者（South African Male Survivors of Sexual Abuse）」指，南非每年發生超過50萬宗強姦案，當中近10萬宗強姦案的受害人是男性。</strong>該組織在網頁提到，一個於2002年進行的美國研究曾披露，每8名強姦受害人中便有1人是男性，而英國另一個研究更表示，每6名男子中便有1名男子曾被性侵甚至是強姦。<br />\n<br />\n而早於2004年，英國傳媒已報道南非不斷發生男性被強姦案件，其中高大、健碩及英俊的男性有可能成為被強姦目標，而即使男性的身體狀況未能進行性行為，施暴的女性都會以各種手段，包括權藥或身體接觸，令受害男性進入狀態，然後將他們強姦。<br />\n<br />\n另有多篇報道表示，部分強姦男人的女性，因曾被施暴或從事性工作時感染愛滋病毒，故強姦男性讓對方感染愛滋病毒，以散播愛滋作為進行報復。而英國《每日電訊報》於2004年報道，一名39歲男子下班等巴士時，在巴士站被多名婦人擄走輪姦，其中一人更對他說「歡迎來到愛滋世界」（Welcome to the world of AIDS.）。而另一名18歲男生被強姦後，證實感染愛滋。"},{"pid":"a43a0c11c6f085eac2203078e75756a4bdcb3acc","tid":505424,"uid":4052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"快點強姦樓主"},{"pid":"a989f603467c043ff61eec97b30864a2683cefa5","tid":505424,"uid":69221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"每8名強姦受害人中便有1人是男性，而英國另一個研究更表示，每6名男子中便有1名男子曾被性侵甚至是強姦<br />\n有冇數學家計下幾多%女人俾人強姦過"},{"pid":"bc074011ba07b1abac3d38797dd0dc8a4af3c0b6","tid":505424,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"#metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ac5833c9166659ef55af6cdf9e790591bcadd9","tid":505424,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T23:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32116be60e744bafa87dad9c960fa058b3a69770","tid":505424,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T00:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df61ae9c1ca2d88e91b8ebb425828ae4abe53e3b","tid":505424,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T00:38:02.000Z","msg":"靚仔想報復<br />\n可找我雞姦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab4f8de954245805a71c4e011d1c6fe40c54ec9","tid":505424,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T00:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚仔想報復<br />\n可找我雞姦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw 請用dom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a24d5866ab0634ab2191c4f7b8e509b3545bb65","tid":505424,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T00:40:01.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"0d60424521d6357848c14e8b7147d5c26fd18f15","tid":505424,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T00:43:30.000Z","msg":"一名39歲男子下班等巴士時，在巴士站被多名婦人擄走輪姦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b563e489c4cabfa68cd82abea75a56fdb78524","tid":505424,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T00:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162ddbbcb0f0e439508e08b2c9003bec6043078f","tid":505424,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c24bbda885514fc6a50d0204a9c040b64fc0d6","tid":505424,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"強姦完有愛滋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}